MRS. REED is skeletal thin and tall. Taller than Reed. Her
skin is wrinkled and blotted. Infected? She wears the
physical conditions of a 200 year old human on the body of a
middle aged woman. A PURPLE VEIL hides her sunken complexion.
Her brittle hands carry what appears to be BLUEBERRY PIE...
PAXTON
Mrs. Reed? Can we help you?
MRS. REED painstakingly sets the BLUEBERRY PIE onto the card
