horror as Mrs. Reed moves over to the far wall. She never
utters a word. Just the unnerving rasp of her BREATHING.
Paxton goes to help, but Barnes stops her.
BARNES
Wait.
Mrs. Reed lowers herself onto the floor. She moans in pain,
